ted-posts":[{"id":10872,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/02\/ahl-al-kitab-believers\/","url_meta":{"origin":32431,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Ahl Kitab: Among People of the Book are righteous believers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 2, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, delayed the evening prayer, then he later came out to the mosque to find people waiting for the prayer. The Prophet said, \u201cAre there none among the people of these religions remembering Allah at this hour besides\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17044,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/11\/25\/sahabah-ten-ayat-ilm-amal\/","url_meta":{"origin":32431,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Companions learn ten verses at a time","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 25, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Abdur Rahman reported: The companions would learn to recite ten verses from the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him. They would not take another ten verses until they understood the knowledge and deeds they contained. They would say, \"We learned sacred knowledge and action together.\" Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35837,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/27\/ten-verses-at-night\/","url_meta":{"origin":32431,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Ten verses at night, not among heedless","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 27, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever recites ten verses in the night will never be recorded among the negligent.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n 2003 Grade: Sahih li ghayrihi (authentic due to external evidence) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32703,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/07\/ali-three-baqarah-before-bed\/","url_meta":{"origin":32431,"position":3},"title":"Ali on Quran: Recite last three verses of al-Baqarah before bed","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 7, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Ishaq reported: Ali, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cI have not seen anyone of intelligence go to sleep until he had recited these three verses at the end of Surat al-Baqarah.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Da\u0304rimi\u0304 3289 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Nawawi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0625\u0650\u0633\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0627\u0642 \u0639\u0646 \u0639\u0644\u064a\u0651\u064d \u0631\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3886,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/29\/surah-mulk-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":32431,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Surat al-Mulk intercedes for reciters","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 29, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere is a chapter in the Quran, not but thirty verses, which will argue on behalf of its companion until he is admitted into Paradise. It is the chapter, 'Blessed is He...'\u201d (67:1) Source: al-Mu\u2019jam\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41145,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/09\/07\/last-two-ayat-arsh\/","url_meta":{"origin":32431,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Last two verses of al-Baqarah from the Throne","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 7, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Hudhayfah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cI have been given these last two verses of Surat al-Baqarah from the treasures beneath the Throne. No prophet has been given the likes of them before me.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 23251 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt